quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif Laam Miim
  2,2,"This is the book in which there is nothing doubtful, (there is) guidance (in it) for those who guard (against evil)"
  2,3,who believe in the unseen and establish worship (salat) and spend from that which We have provided for them
  2,4,"and who believe in that which is sent down to you and that which was sent down before you, and are certain about the hereafter"
  2,5,Those are on guidance from their Lord and those are the persons who are successful
  2,6,"For those who do not believe, it is the same to them, whether you warn them or do not warn them they will certainly not believe"
  2,7,"God has set a seal upon their hearts and upon their hearings, and upon their eyes is a covering, and for them there is a great punishment"